    "Regarding data scale, the performance of CPMI-ChatGLM reached its peak at a data volume of 3 k and declined with further increases.",
    "This trend may be attributed to the diversity of the data.",
    "In addition, we also investigated the influence of instruction data on model performance and conducted a comparative analysis among various commonly employed LLMs.",
    "Through a comprehensive evaluation combining both automatic metrics and human evaluation, we demonstrated the superiority of CPMI-ChatGLM.",
    "Considering resource and cost limitations, we selected a set of 3096 meticulously labeled data for fine-tuning CPMI-ChatGLM."
